Step 1: 
     Go to Tablix Properties has the Repeat header columns on each page ticked.

Step 2:
      Go to Grouping in bottom.
      Right Side Column Goup Click Arrow And Select (Advanced Mode).

Step 3: Go to Right Side In Grouping in Rows Group
        Click 2nd Static 
        Open properties  Showing This 
                          { Select this Last 2 only 
                            FixedData=False
                            KeepTogether=False
                            KeepWithGroup = After
                            RepeatOnNewPage=True
                            }
